    <statement>
        
        
        
                <p>
                    Assignments are about to be made for 7 distinct roles in the upcoming play at Spring Hill SchoolSandalwood Elementary. During auditions, 11 people tried out. How many different castings are possible?
                </p> 
        <p>

        </p>
        <p>
        Show all of your steps, specify which formula you used, and state why you used it.
        </p>
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p> We are selecting 7 from a total of 11 possibilities (without repeats), and the order of the selections matters. There are <m>_{11}P_{7}</m> <m> = 1663200</m> possibilities.</p>
    </answer>
